					<h1>Health Resource Centre (Library)</h1>
<p><img title="HRC entrance off atrium" border="0" alt="HRC entrance off atrium" align="right" src="/export/sites/brandonrha/galleries/img/Health_Centre_pics/HRC_entrance_off_atrium.jpg" width="325" height="251" /></p>
<div align="justify">
<p>Located on the main floor of the Clinical Services Building at the Brandon Regional Health Centre. <br />
150 McTavish Avenue East&nbsp; <br />
Brandon, Manitoba <br />
R7A 2B3</p>
<p class="content">Ph: (204) 578-4080 <br />
Fax: (204) 578-4984 <br />
Email: <a href="mailto:brhalib@brandonrha.mb.ca"><u>library@brandonrha.mb.ca</u> </a></p>
<p class="content">Health Resource Centre Manager <br />
Wendy Wareham</p>
<p class="content">Regular Hours: <br />
Monday - Friday 8:00 - 4:30 <br />
Closed weekends and statutory holidays.</p>
<p class="content"><img title="Health Resource Centre" border="0" alt="Health Resource Centre" align="right" src="/export/sites/brandonrha/galleries/img/Health_Centre_pics/Health_Resource_Centre.jpg" />The Brandon RHA Health Resource Centre (Library) collection contains a variety of medical, nursing, consumer health and allied health resources including books, journals and videos.&nbsp; <br />
<br />
Items in our Consumer Health Collection may be borrowed by anyone living in the Westman area. <br />
<br />
The Library staff are dedicated to providing patients, families and community members with the tools and skills they need to manage their health decisions.</p>
<p class="content">Our services include:</p>
<ul>
    <li>
    <div class="content">Assistance finding current and accurate health information</div>
    </li>
    <li>
    <div class="content">Five computers with Internet access</div>
    </li>
    <li>
    <div class="content">Two TVs with DVDs and VCRs</div>
    </li>
    <li>
    <div class="content">Reading area and two private rooms for quiet study <br />
    &nbsp;</div>
    </li>
</ul>
